Depends: ${perl:Depends}, libdevice-serialport-perl (>= 1.00), libtext-lookuptable-perl (>= 0.03-1)
Description: Perl5 module for communicating with a MegaSquirt controller
 Device::MegaSquirt provides operations for communicating with a MegaSquirt
 controller [http://www.msextra.com].  Operations such as reading/writing tables,
 reading live data, and writing configuration variables.

